text: Růžena Beinhauerová (23 September 1912 - 16 May 1968) was a Czech alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:1968 deaths Category:Czech female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ostrava
